body.description: Cascade Complete ActionPacs dishwasher detergent powers away even 24-hour stuck-on messes for a complete clean. That's because every ActionPac has 25% more Cleaning Power* (*% cleaning ingredients vs. Cascade Original) & is formulated with the grease-fighting power of Dawn dishwashing liquid. Cascade Complete ActionPacs are conveniently premeasured with no finicky wrapping-just toss in a pac. Cascade Complete ActionPacs are phosphate free. Plus, Cascade Complete ActionPacs dissolve quickly to unleash cleaning power early in the cycle. For best results, use Cascade Complete ActionPacs with Cascade Power Dry Rinse Aid for powerful drying and Cascade Dishwasher Cleaner to keep your dishwasher machine sparkling. Save up to 15 gallons of water per dishwasher load when you skip the pre-wash and run your dishwasher with Cascade Complete ActionPacs. Cascade is the #1 Recommended Brand in North America** **More dishwasher brands in North America recommend Cascade vs. any other automatic dishwashing detergent brand, recommendations as part of co-marketing agreements.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Messy but that's on me
reviews.reviewText: I have a countertop (Novete) dishwasher and can't seem to find small pods that are suitable for that size. I bought these and they work just fine .... BUT ... I cut them open & squish them into a Tupperware container; mix up the dry & liquid & use like ONE HALF TEASPOON ONLY!!!! I saw a review that said NOT to put it in FIRST ... well, yah, I DO ANYWAY & still get soapy water to wash dishes even after that first little cycle of water comes into the base ... I'm thinking that's the heating part & when it starts to swing into motion, that is what dissolves the detergent & it goes to town. My dishes come out super clean & I like the combo detergent. I tried just powder --- ended up with water spots on everything. I washed a small pan from my toaster oven & it came out nasty; still useable, but maybe not made for dishwashers of this size. Now the quest is on to find detergent LIKE THIS in the little pods for little dishwashers. CASCADE ... are you up to the challenge? This is a great detergent & even though a messy process for now, it does a great job of cleaning.
